It was a great spine tingling thriller!  But they should have left the sex scene in there.  It's not for the very young though.

A very gritty murder movie with a very bestial killer. An extremely likeable hero. Scenes of raw depravity. A killer that disgusts you and makes you rout for the good guy! An ending that somewhat satisfies in its complexity.
